item.title: ZAMP 329 – Scouts Guide to the Zombie Apocalypse
item.description: You know what's AWESOME!… Scouting! Or rather, Scouts Guide to the Zombie Apocalypse. Listen to us discuss and ponder about this 10-year-old gem that people seem to have missed out on. Hear about the trampoline scene and the cat lady scene. Feed: https://zombiesatemypodcast.com/feed/podcast/

item.title: 159 - Sad Happy - Circa Waves - Audio Judo
item.description: Matthew and Kyle talk about the "happy" side of the double album "Sad Happy" from 2020 by the alternative band, Circa Waves. Do you really want to see what we look like while we record?
